&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;em>1. अजीर्णे भोजनं विषम् ।&lt;/em>
If previously taken Lunch is not digested..taking Dinner will be equivalent to taking Poison. Hunger is one signal that the previous food is digested&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;em>2. अर्धरोगहरी निद्रा ।&lt;/em>
Proper sleep cures half of the diseases..&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;em>3 मुद्गदाली गदव्याली ।&lt;/em>
Of all the Pulses, Green grams are the best. It boosts Immunity. Other Pulses all have one or the other side effects.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Don't Be Afraid Of Covid</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/dont-be-afraid-of-covid/</link><pubDate>Sat, 15 May 2021 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/dont-be-afraid-of-covid/</guid><description>&lt;p>
